e projects. This makes it an ideal book for any auditor encountering the Agile methodology, and any Agile teams preparing for a management audit. This book will enable you to: understand the principles of Agile appreciate how it might be effectively audited improve communication between the auditor and the Agile team. Read this book to understand how to get the most out of Agile audits, whatever your role.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 07. Mrz 2024) 0aAgile software development. 0aAuditing. 7aCOMPUTERS / Desktop Applications / Project Management Software.2bisacsh  aAgile.  aIT Audit.  aProject management.  aagile methodologies.  aagile team.  aaudit.  aauditing.  agovernance.  ainternal audit.0 cEPUBz978184928589640uhttps://sciendo.com/book/9781849285889  aGBV-deGruyter-alles